							<h1 class="alert-bar__title h2">
					Miscarriage reports raise urgent concerns for pregnant women in ICE custody.				</h1>
			
					<div class="alert-bar__description h6">
				<p>Congress has the responsibility to conduct oversight, bear witness, and demand transparency. If conditions are humane, ICE should have nothing to hide. Add your name to demand accountability now.</p>
			</div>
		
